Town of [Greater London](/Greater_London)

This article is about the town in south-east London. For the town in east London, which, with typical human lack of imagination, shares a name, see [Bromley-by-Bow](/Bromley-by-Bow). For the administrative district that encompasses this particular sprawl, see [London Borough of Bromley](/London_Borough_of_Bromley). For other instances of this rather uninspired placename, consult [Bromley (disambiguation)](/Bromley_(disambiguation)); I assume you have nothing better to do.

